{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc17-714-whats-new-in-apple-pay-and-wallet"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"metadata":{"title":"What’s New in Apple Pay & Wallet","role":"sampleCode","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"roleHeading":"WWDC17"},"sections":[],"sampleCodeDownload":{"kind":"sampleDownload","action":{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/wwdc17\/714","overridingTitle":"Watch Video (49 min)"}},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"anchor":"Whats-new-with-Wallet","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"What’s new with Wallet"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"mass deletion interface for your passes"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"lighter color scheme","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"from iOS 11, only encrypted NFC passes are supported. Register yours at "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/apple-pay\/"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"anchor":"Opt-out-of-sharing","type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Opt-out of sharing"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Passes can now be opted-out of sharing"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Useful for single-use items, like loyalty cards or tickets","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"To take advantage of this, set the new top-level ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"sharingProhibited"},{"text":" key with value ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"text":" in your ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"pass.json"},{"text":":","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"json","code":["{","  ...","  \"sharingProhibited\": true,","  ...","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"style":"note","name":"Note","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Users can still share the pass in older versions of iOS."}]}]},{"anchor":"Written-By","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Written By"},{"columns":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"zntfdr"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"size":1},{"content":[{"text":"zntfdr","level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"zntfdr"},{"inlineContent":[{"overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Contributed Notes"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/zntfdr","overridingTitle":"Contributed Notes","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"|","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/zntfdr","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"|","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"size":4}],"numberOfColumns":5,"type":"row"},{"type":"thematicBreak"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Missing anything? Corrections? "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Related-Sessions","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Related Sessions"},{"style":"list","type":"links","items":["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC18-720-Wallet-and-Apple-Pay-Creating-Great-Customer-Experiences","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17-718-Introducing-Core-NFC","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC16-703-Apple-Pay-on-the-Web","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC16-704-Whats-New-with-Wallet-and-Apple-Pay"]},{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Legal Notice"}],"type":"strong"}],"type":"small"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All content copyright © 2012 – 2025 Apple Inc. All rights reserved."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Swift, the Swift logo, Swift Playgrounds, Xcode, Instruments, Cocoa Touch, Touch ID, FaceID, iPhone, iPad, Safari, Apple Vision, Apple Watch, App Store, iPadOS, watchOS, visionOS, tvOS, Mac, and macOS are trademarks of Apple Inc., registered in the U.S. and other countries."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This website is not made by, affiliated with, nor endorsed by Apple."}],"type":"small"}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"article","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17-714-Whats-New-in-Apple-Pay-and-Wallet","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Apple Pay is the easy and secure way to accept payments in your app and website on iPhone, iPad, Apple Watch, and Mac. Get the latest news and updates from the Wallet and Apple Pay teams. New for this year, increase your conversions by providing feedback to users right in the Apple Pay sheet. Discover great new Wallet features like pass sharing controls, and increase customer satisfaction and sales with UI best practices."}],"references":{"WWDC17-Icon.png":{"alt":null,"identifier":"WWDC17-Icon.png","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17-Icon.png"}],"type":"image"},"WWDCNotes.png":{"type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDCNotes.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"alt":null,"identifier":"WWDCNotes.png"},"https://wwdcnotes.com/documentation/wwdcnotes/contributing":{"url":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"Contributions are welcome!","type":"text"}],"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","type":"link","title":"Contributions are welcome!"},"zntfdr.jpeg":{"alt":null,"identifier":"zntfdr.jpeg","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/zntfdr.jpeg"}],"type":"image"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC18-720-Wallet-and-Apple-Pay-Creating-Great-Customer-Experiences":{"role":"sampleCode","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC18-720-Wallet-and-Apple-Pay-Creating-Great-Customer-Experiences","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc18-720-wallet-and-apple-pay-creating-great-customer-experiences","abstract":[{"text":"Get the latest news and updates from the Wallet and Apple Pay team. Learn how iPhone and Apple Watch can power innovative commerce experiences. Hear about the latest design best practices for Apple Pay. And discover how to create your own contactless passes for rewards cards, gift cards, tickets and more.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","title":"Wallet and Apple Pay: Creating Great Customer Experiences","kind":"article"},"WWDC17.jpeg":{"type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17.jpeg","traits":["1x","light"]}],"alt":null,"identifier":"WWDC17.jpeg"},"zntfdr":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/zntfdr.jpeg","traits":["1x","light"]}],"identifier":"zntfdr","type":"image","alt":"Profile image of zntfdr"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC17-718-Introducing-Core-NFC":{"kind":"article","type":"topic","title":"Introducing Core NFC","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc17-718-introducing-core-nfc","abstract":[{"text":"Core NFC is an exciting new framework that enables you to read NFC tags in your apps on iPhone 7 and iPhone 7 Plus.  Learn how to integrate Core NFC into your apps, key requirements for using this feature, and start thinking about the new kinds of apps that are enabled with NFC capabilities.","type":"text"}],"role":"sampleCode","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17-718-Introducing-Core-NFC"},"https://":{"identifier":"https:\/\/","title":"Blog","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Blog"}],"url":"https:\/\/","type":"link"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC16-703-Apple-Pay-on-the-Web":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"This year, Apple Pay is coming to the web with Safari on both macOS and iOS. Now you can experience the convenience and security of Apple Pay in your store, in your app, and on your website. Discover how easy it is to set up Apple Pay on the web, and learn how designing for Apple Pay can increase conversions, user engagement, and customer satisfaction."}],"type":"topic","role":"sampleCode","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc16-703-apple-pay-on-the-web","title":"Apple Pay on the Web","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC16-703-Apple-Pay-on-the-Web","kind":"article"},"https://github.com/zntfdr":{"type":"link","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/zntfdr","title":"GitHub","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"GitHub","type":"text"}],"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/zntfdr"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC16-704-Whats-New-with-Wallet-and-Apple-Pay":{"kind":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC16-704-Whats-New-with-Wallet-and-Apple-Pay","role":"sampleCode","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc16-704-whats-new-with-wallet-and-apple-pay","type":"topic","title":"What’s New with Wallet and Apple Pay","abstract":[{"text":"Get the latest news and updates from the Wallet and Apple Pay teams. Learn how to integrate Apple Pay into more places than ever before including watchOS, iOS Messages and Intents extensions. Learn about new tools to make testing and developing your Apple Pay-enabled apps even easier. We’ll also cover new features in Wallet for retailers, banks, and card issuers.","type":"text"}]},"https://developer.apple.com/apple-pay/":{"url":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/apple-pay\/","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"developer.apple.com\/apple-pay","type":"text"}],"identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/apple-pay\/","type":"link","title":"developer.apple.com\/apple-pay"},"https://developer.apple.com/wwdc17/714":{"identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/wwdc17\/714","url":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/wwdc17\/714","type":"download","checksum":null},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes":{"title":"WWDC Notes","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"WWDCNotes.png"}],"role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","abstract":[{"text":"Session notes shared by the community for the community.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/zntfdr":{"title":"zntfdr (332 notes)","abstract":[{"text":"No Bio on GitHub","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/zntfdr","kind":"article","images":[{"type":"card","identifier":"zntfdr.jpeg"},{"type":"icon","identifier":"zntfdr.jpeg"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/zntfdr","role":"sampleCode"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC17":{"title":"WWDC17","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc17","images":[{"identifier":"WWDC17-Icon.png","type":"icon"},{"identifier":"WWDC17.jpeg","type":"card"}],"role":"collectionGroup","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17","abstract":[{"text":"Xcode 9, Swift 4.0, iOS 11, macOS 10.13 (High Sierra), tvOS 11, watchOS 4.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"New APIs: ","type":"text"},{"code":"Core NFC","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and more.","type":"text"}],"kind":"article","type":"topic"}}}